UID:TDjZU_fJhsjRXgj-qyM2N
SUMMARY:Mead tasting
DTSTAMP:20260205T082835Z
DTSTART:20260215T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Ballard (5.3 miles NW)\n\nMead is a fermented drink made with h
	oney. A $45 ticket includes 6 tastes of Washington meads (2.5 ounces each)
	 with snacks for sale at the Winter Mead Festival at Skål Beer Hall\, 5429
	 Ballard Ave. NW in Seattle for age 21+. No pets. Repeats several times a 
	year.\n\nFrom Events12 Seattle
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/winter-mead-festival-at-skal-beer-hall-tic
	kets-1980140350091
