BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:HPp0p1Ee8zBudKuaNokYr
SUMMARY:Voice Division Recital
DTSTAMP:20260205T082835Z
DTSTART:20260218T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Tuesday\, Feb 17\, 2026\, 4 p.m. PST\n\nUWvoice students of Tho
	mas Harper and Carrie Shaw perform art songs and arias from the vocal repe
	rtoire.\n\nFREE admission\n\nCampus location:  Music Building \\(MUS\\) Ca
	mpus room: Brechemin Auditorium Accessibility Contact: To request disabili
	ty accommodation contact the Disability Services Office at least ten days 
